Package org.odpi.openmetadata.opentypes

package org.odpi.openmetadata.opentypes
This package contains the open metadata types definition. There is one class for each release.
  • OpenMetadataTypesArchive - add new types for current release here. They can be changed until moved to a specific release class.
  • OpenMetadataTypesArchive1_3 - types added for 1.3 release
  • OpenMetadataTypesArchive1_2 - types added for releases before 1.3
  • Related Packages

    Description
    org.odpi.openmetadata.opentypes.utility
    This package contains a utility for writing open metadata types.
